<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٠٦٨ - غُنْدَرٌ، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ، عَنْ أَبِي هَاشِمٍ، عَنِ الْحَارِثِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«يَتَزَوَّجُ الْحُرُّ مِنَ الْإِمَاءِ أَرْبَعَةً»</span> وَقَالَ حَمَّادٌ: <span class="c2">«اثْنَتَيْنِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>